ail Systems Limited in May 2023. Titagarh Rail Systems Limited was incorporated in 1997 and is based in Kolkata, India.", "fullTimeEmployees": 1222, "companyOfficers": [{"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Jagdish Prasad Chowdhary B.Com., MIMA", "age": 85, "title": "Executive Chairman", "yearBorn": 1940, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 35700000, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Umesh  Chowdhary B.Com.", "age": 51, "title": "Vice Chairman, MD & CEO", "yearBorn": 1974, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 35700000, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Saurav  Singhania", "age": 40, "title": "CFO, Group Finance Controller & Chief Risk Officer", "yearBorn": 1985, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 9600000, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Anil Kumar Agarwal B.Com. ACA, CWA", "age": 50, "title": "Deputy MD & Director", "yearBorn": 1975, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 19400000, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Prithish  Chowdhary", "age": 24, "title": "Deputy MD & Whole-Time Director", "yearBorn": 2001, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 10200000, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Aditya  Purohit", "title": "Company Secretary & Compliance Officer", "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Devendra Kumar Vyas ACA, B. COM.", "age": 56, "title": "Chief Executive Officer of Freight Rail Systems", "yearBorn": 1969, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Vijay  Subramanian", "title": "Chief Transformation Officer & CEO of Passenger Rail Systems", "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}], "compensationAsOfEpochDate": 1767139200, "irWebsite": "http://www.titagarh.biz/financials.html", "executiveTeam": [], "maxAge": 86400, "priceHint": 2, "previousClose": 621.65, "open": 629.7, "dayLow": 